OL,6,FA man from Swindon who pretended to be
OL,7,Fa taxi driver in order to pick up a
OL,8,Fvulnerable woman has been found guilty
OL,9,Fof rape for a second time.
OL,11,FFareed Tariq, 43, of Barnum Court, had
OL,12,Falready been jailed for rape in 2012.
OL,14,FThis time, posing as a taxi driver, he
OL,15,Ftook the woman to a quiet area and
OL,16,Fraped her.
