OL,6,FDS Emma Kinderman, from CID, said:
OL,7,F"This was a horrendous incident, where
OL,8,FTariq pretended to be a taxi driver
OL,9,Fand picked up a vulnerable woman after
OL,10,Fa night out.
OL,12,F"He took her to a quiet area and raped
OL,13,Fher before picking up her son from her
OL,14,Ffriend's house.
OL,16,F"This is the second time that Tariq
OL,17,Fhas been found guilty of raping a
OL,18,Fwoman after a night out. He was jailed
OL,19,Ffor six years in 2012.
