OL,6,F"Our trained officers and partner
OL,7,Forganisations are here to listen and
OL,8,Fwork together to support you in any
OL,9,Fway we can.
OL,11,F"Importantly, your information could
OL,12,Fhelp us bring the offender to justice
OL,13,Fand make sure you, and other people in
OL,14,Fa similar situation, are kept safe."
OL,16,FTariq was found guilty by a majority
OL,17,Fverdict on Monday 19 February at
OL,18,FSwindon Crown Court following a trial.
